			    <h2 id="shipping">Shipping</h2>

			    <ul class="list-faqs">
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>Order and Shipping Confirmation</h3>
			    		<p>You will receive an email confirmation once your order has been successfully placed that includes your order number and shipping method. Please make sure your shipping address is correct, as we are unable to redirect goods once they are en route. Orders can take up to 3 days to be processed and shipped. Once your order is prepared for shipment you will receive a confirmation email with your tracking information.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>Where We Ship</h3>
						<p>We ship to US delivery addresses within the contiguous 48 states.</p>

						<p>We also ship to Alaska, Hawaii and APO/FPO addresses when they have a US zip code. Additional shipping charges may apply, and delivery may take longer to these locations.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>Shipping Costs</h3>
			    		<p>Standard Ground Shipping within the US is $5.95 for orders below $49, and free for orders over $49 after coupons, rebates and discounts.</p>
			    		<p>Please note that order processing may take up to 2 business days after the order is placed. Second day delivery may not be available for orders placed on, or requested to be delivered on, Saturdays, Sundays or holidays. The availability of Second day delivery will always be subject to availability of stock, subject to a surcharge and be dependent on where the delivery location is.</p>
			    		<p>Shipping to Alaska, Hawaii, US Territories, and APO/FPO addresses standard is $14.95 and free for orders over $49 after coupons, rebate and discounts.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>Taxes</h3>
			    		<p>Taxes are calculated according to shipping destination.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>When will my order ship?</h3>
			    		<p>Unless there is an unusual circumstance, our aim is to process your order within 48 hours. At that point it typically takes 3 days for the order to arrive.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>How long will it take to ship to Alaska, Hawaii, and Puerto Rico?</h3>
			    		<p>Typically, it will take 7-10 days. We work diligently to shorten that time as much as we possibly can.</p>
                  </li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>How do I track my order?</h3>

			    		<p>Each order is assigned a tracking number that will be sent to you when we confirm your order has been received, and again when it is about to ship. Once shipped, use that tracking number until you receive your ordered. Sometimes order progress takes a day or so before it is reported via the link.</p>
			    	</li>
			    	<li>
			    		<h3>How can I edit my shipping address?</h3>

			    		<p>When the Ship To designation is on your screen, simply delete the previous information and enter the new address.</p>
			    	</li>
			    </ul>

