				<h2>Billing</h2>

				<ul class="list-faqs">
					<li>
						<h3>When will my credit card be charged?</h3>

						<p>Your credit card will be charged as soon as your order is confirmed.</p>
					</li>

					<li>
						<h3>Can I remove a saved payment method?</h3>

						<p>Yes. You can simply delete the saved method from your customer information. If you have difficulty with this, please <a href="mailto:info@prioriskincare.com">contact Customer Service</a>.</p>
					</li>


					<li>
						<h3>What forms of payment do you accept?</h3>

						<p>We accept online payments by Visa, MasterCard, American Express or PayPal. When purchasing from Priori your financial details are passed through a secure server using the latest 128-bit SSL (secure socket layer) encryption technology. Credit card details are never stored on the Priori website in any way, and are passed on directly to our Payment Gateway (Stripe or PayPal) for authorization and authentication.</p>
					</li>


					<li>
						<h3>What can I do if my payment is declined?</h3>

						<p>If you believe your payment method has been declined erroneously you can contact your provider, or <a href="mailto:info@prioriskincare.com">contact us</a>, and we will try to find another solution.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>

