				<h2>Returns + Exchanges</h2>

			    <ul class="list-faqs">
                 	<li>
                      <h3>Easy 30-Day Returns</h3>
						<p>PRIORI stands behind the quality of our products, and we hope you are happy with your order. If you are not satisfied for any reason, simply return your item(s) within 30 days of purchase for a full refund, minus shipping. </p>
                      	<p>Returning your PRIORI order is free and easy. For your convenience, our Customer Service team will provide a pre-paid label upon email request. Returns and exchanges are accepted within 30 days of order date. A full refund, excluding shipping charges, will be issued on unused items once we receive your return. Please keep a record of your return tracking.</p> 	
                      <p>Please note: only items purchased on prioriskincare.com may be accepted for return or exchange. If you purchased your items in a salon or through an authorized retailer, please contact them for their return policy.</p>
                  </li>

					<li>
						<h3>Return Shipping</h3>
                      <p>Email PRIORI Skincare Customer Service at <a href="info@prioriskincare.com">info@prioriskincare.com</a>  for us to send you a pre-paid return shipping label.</p>
					</li>

					<li>
						<h3>Late Returns</h3>
						<p>Any item returned after 30 days from order date is not eligible for refund.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Receiving a Refund</h3>

						<p>A refund will be issued once we have received your returned items. Refunds do not include any shipping or handling charges. Your refund will be credited to the credit card used for the original transaction. Please note that credit card refunds may take up to 10 business day for your bank to complete, depending on their processing times. This can vary greatly between credit card issuers</p>
					</li>

					<li>
						<h3>What should I do if I receive the wrong product?</h3>

                      <p>We’re sorry about that. You can either call <a href="tel:+18006058564">(800 605-8564)</a>, or email our <a href="info@prioriskincare.com">Customer Service team</a>, and we will walk you through the steps to correct this error.</p>
					</li>
				</ul>

